OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will feed in across many northern
OL,7,Fand western areas overnight,
OL,8,Faccompanied by brisk winds. Elsewhere
OL,9,Fshowers will fade to leave a mostly
OL,10,Fdry night with clear spells and a few
OL,11,Fmist patches. Remaining frost-free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FThe southeast will be dry with
OL,14,Fsome warm sunshine. A band of rain
OL,15,Fwill move eastwards across remaining
OL,16,Fareas, giving way to sunshine, but
OL,17,Fwith blustery showers in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
